The paper proposes a new approach for local feature learning for image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach involves learning discriminative and shareable features, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses exemplar selection methods, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
